{"tid":1503370,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"新屋嶺情況係點呢？","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T03:42:14.000Z","uid":265246,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cad2858c932f4f689a77c663f228d1ca50aac313","tid":1503370,"uid":265246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"時至今日被捕的人數多達600人 情況是怎樣呢 <br />\n只有零聲聲音收到不同情度的對待、盤問、刑罰、追究&hellip;等等。<br />\n了解到可能有些人仕已經進入司法情序，但都只是制度上的問題，但幾百多位人仕不是少數目，他們的處景是怎樣呢、心理上有沒有得到援助呢，法律上又有冇呢？！每次行動完都有維數不少的人被拉，但又好似冇消息跟進 每次又有新一批被拉又繼續冇消息。媒體又好像只針對制度。如果大家有任何消息，方便的話請告之或向公眾發放。<br />\n彰顯公義 有勞。Thank you"},{"pid":"e59193c23347deff90a8f144a71f9a54d18a59be","tid":1503370,"uid":9253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da654cd1876fe2accfd3588df9ef6e831349d889","tid":1503370,"uid":9253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:18:20.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"cac6d6d38d772e185de7328e814d5cca91e8d177","tid":1503370,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:18:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"4e5db18fcb9496c9c8aab3df067b590124b0d3cc","tid":1503370,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEhtr